metadata.name: 𝐀 𝐒𝐦𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐁𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐤
metadata.description:
Heads exploding, arms ripped off...
Well, at some point it starts getting tiring, and for Rose, nothing's better than a hot bath with kittens to relax.


✧All bidders will receive a treasure map to join our treasure hunt event.✧
